---
title: Greek-Inspired Chicken Pasta with Creamy Sauce and Feta
description: We've taken the classic flavours of Greek cuisine and translated them into a creamy fusilli that the whole family will love – packed with juicy tomatoes and crisp green peppers. And better yet, it will be ready to eat in no time!
